    "en": "The British Museum Collection comprises nearly 5 million objects documenting two million years of human history and culture from across six continents. Collection online provides searchable access to over 2 million catalogued records with high-definition images, covering archaeology, art, cultural artifacts, and historical objects. The database represents over 40 years of cataloguing work and continues to expand daily.",
